{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1681-05_147","head":{"value":"[Naissance de Mars, en Vers]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mai 1681 [tome 5], p. 147-153.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Rien n’est plus connu que les deux Divinitez de la Guerre. Tout le monde sçait que Pallas est née de Jupiter seul, qui la fit sortir toute armée de son cerveau ; mais il y a peut-estre des Gens qui ne sçavent pas que selon Ovide, Mars est né de Junon seule. La Personne de qualité dont je vous fis voir dans ma Lettre de Fevrier la Métamorphose d’Alectrion, a décrit cette Avanture de ce mesme stile dont vous fustes si contente.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"label":{"value":"NAISSANCE DE MARS.","id":"/div/quote/label"},"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lors qu’avec un coup de Marteau","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#1":{"value":"(","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Maniere d’accoucher nouvelle &amp; surprenante","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":")","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#2"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jupiter autrefois tira de son cerveau","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pallas qui fut d’abord &amp; guerriere &amp; sçavante ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Junon fut sur le point de créver de dépit,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De voir qu’il avoit eu l’esprit","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De mettre au jour, sans secours de Femelle,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une Pouponne &amp; si sage &amp; si belle.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jalouse d’un si beau destin,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui d’abord sur son teint mit une couleur pâle,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle jura de perdre son Latin,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou de faire si bien, qu’enfin","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle mettroit au jour quelque Poupon sans Mâle.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour cet effet, dés le moment,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle se résolut d’aller diligemment","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/hi/#"}}},{"#":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#[0]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Consulter l’Ocean","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" (","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#[2]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Oncle de la Déesse","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#[3]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":")","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#[4]/#"}}]},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui dans son extréme vieillesse","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Passoit pour estre un Dieu de rare entendement ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais comme sa demeure estoit un peu lointaine,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[18]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que Junon s’engagea dans ce voyage à pié","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[19]/hi/#"}}},{"#1":{"value":"(","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car un Paon de son Char estoit estropié","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":")","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[20]/#2"}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On s’imaginera sans peine","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[21]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/d